                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36440222/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2015-10-27 22:59
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="43773816">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dolai/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2468525-3.jpg" alt="Jason" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43773816/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43773816/" class="">第141页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dolai/" class=" " title="Jason">Jason</a>
                (谦谦君子，温润如玉。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="43773816">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">摘抄：如果政治哲学家不准备去捍卫他们所认为正当的价值，那么他们就决不能获致那种必须从整体上加以判断的综合性框架。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-09 13:19</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>摘抄：如果政治哲学家不准备去捍卫他们所认为正当的价值，那么他们就决不能获致那种必须从整体上加以判断的综合性框架。</p>
